            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 italic">"Fitur stok ini penyelamat. Saya tahu persis kapan harus restock Indomie dan minyak goreng tanpa hitung manual."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <img alt="Kak Maya" class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full object-cover" src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg" />
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Kak Maya</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Maya Coffee, Surabaya</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">star</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 italic">"Tim support-nya sangat profesional. Waktu saya ada pertanyaan setup printer, mereka bantu via WhatsApp langsung."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <section id="pricing" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Harga Terjangkau untuk Semua</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">27% lebih murah dari kompetitor dengan fitur lebih lengkap</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Gratis -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Gratis</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Untuk mulai bisnis kecil</p>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Rp 0</div>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">selamanya</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-slate-600 text-sm">
